member.name: P:TurtleGeek.Roster.TurtleFileAttachment.FullFileName
member.summary: When the TurtleFileAttachment object is new (that is, before the object has been saved), the FullFileName is the original path and file name. Once the Ticket Attachment object has been saved (that is, the file has been copied to our storage folder), the FullFileName is our storage path (.exe path -> TicketId -> TurtleFileAttachmentId -> filename.ext).
